description: Returns a list of information about each flow. For more information, see Deploy a flow in Amazon Bedrock in the Amazon Bedrock User Guide.

parameters.name: flowIdentifier
parameters.description: The unique identifier of the flow.

nested_items.name: flowVersionSummaries
nested_items.description: A list, each member of which contains information about a flow.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: If the total number of results is greater than the maxResults value provided in the request, use this token when making another request in the nextToken field to return the next batch of results.
